<p dir="auto"><a href="https://github.com/csstools/postcss-plugins/tree/main/plugins/css-prefers-color-scheme">Prefers Color Scheme</a> works in all major browsers, including Safari 6+ and
Internet Explorer 9+ without any additional polyfills.</p>
<p dir="auto">To maintain compatibility with browsers supporting <code>prefers-color-scheme</code>, the
library will remove <code>prefers-color-scheme</code> media queries in favor of
cross-browser compatible <code>color</code> media queries. This ensures a seamless
experience, even when JavaScript is unable to run.</p>
<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h3 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">Browser Usage</h3><a id="user-content-browser-usage" class="anchor-element" aria-label="Permalink: Browser Usage" href="#browser-usage"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<p dir="auto">Use <a href="https://github.com/csstools/postcss-plugins/tree/main/plugins/css-prefers-color-scheme">Prefers Color Scheme</a> to activate your <code>prefers-color-scheme</code> queries:</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-js notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="import prefersColorSchemeInit from 'css-prefers-color-scheme/browser';
const prefersColorScheme = prefersColorSchemeInit();"><pre><span class="pl-k">import</span> <span class="pl-s1">prefersColorSchemeInit</span> <span class="pl-k">from</span> <span class="pl-s">'css-prefers-color-scheme/browser'</span><span class="pl-kos">;</span>
<span class="pl-k">const</span> <span class="pl-s1">prefersColorScheme</span> <span class="pl-c1">=</span> <span class="pl-en">prefersColorSchemeInit</span><span class="pl-kos">(</span><span class="pl-kos">)</span><span class="pl-kos">;</span></pre></div>
<p dir="auto">By default, the current OS color scheme is applied if your browser supports it.
Otherwise, the light color scheme is applied. You may override this by passing
in a color scheme.</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-js notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="import prefersColorSchemeInit from 'css-prefers-color-scheme/browser';
const prefersColorScheme = prefersColorSchemeInit('dark');"><pre><span class="pl-k">import</span> <span class="pl-s1">prefersColorSchemeInit</span> <span class="pl-k">from</span> <span class="pl-s">'css-prefers-color-scheme/browser'</span><span class="pl-kos">;</span>
<span class="pl-k">const</span> <span class="pl-s1">prefersColorScheme</span> <span class="pl-c1">=</span> <span class="pl-en">prefersColorSchemeInit</span><span class="pl-kos">(</span><span class="pl-s">'dark'</span><span class="pl-kos">)</span><span class="pl-kos">;</span></pre></div>
<p dir="auto">The <code>prefersColorScheme</code> object returns the following properties — <code>scheme</code>,
<code>hasNativeSupport</code>, <code>onChange</code>, and <code>removeListener</code>.</p>
<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h4 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">scheme</h4><a id="user-content-scheme" class="anchor-element" aria-label="Permalink: scheme" href="#scheme"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<p dir="auto">The <code>scheme</code> property returns the currently preferred color scheme, and it can
be changed.</p>
<div class="highlight highlight-source-js notranslate position-relative overflow-auto" dir="auto" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content="import prefersColorSchemeInit from 'css-prefers-color-scheme/browser';
